Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.21,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.25,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:24.39,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
