Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:33.49,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.30,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:43.04,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
