Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:57.25,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.19,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
