Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H171717&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Print\pos(215,77)}Summer Vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...my script for the summer Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have an audition for a TV anime\nthat starts in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:54.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They said it'll be late night by the time we finish,\nso I don't think I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ask me again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make time for you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:05.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, next time then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako, what part are you reading for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suzuran, the magical kunoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem pretty confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got the script down to a "T."
