Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...so anyway, we're gonna talk about Jung today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jung had a disagreement with Freud, apparently,\nand went in another direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\t(\alpha&H60&)}Jung apparently had a very hard time establishing his ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,243)}We're alone in the park at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&}Then at last he published his theories of psychological types.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...in spite of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&\t(\alpha&H00&)\pos(192,261)}On the basis of these cases...
