Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are frightened of the "Great Mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are also fighting against your "Shadow."
