Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your heart doesn't seem to be in it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get it together, Tatsuhiro Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My instincts are telling me that to get\ntoo close to her is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still don't know anything about her:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:44.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who she really is, or what her\nreal purpose is either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She may be a secret operative of the NHK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Sato, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato! Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hiding away in here as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been drinking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am I not supposed to? I'm over 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By law, I'm allowed to consume alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here's to the law: Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drunks are a pain in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, the rest of the world is on\nsummer vacation already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to be casually shutting yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach! To the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Her face is in my mind for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fact is I don't have swim trunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, I can't do the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't need swim trunks or anything\nto go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For healthy young folk like us, summer\nat the beach can only mean one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Summer Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Summer Comic Stall?
