Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\c&H000000&\shad0\3c&HA7A7A7&\frz358.599\move(-17,206,340,206,0,333)}Comic Stall Venue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, it's the ocean; I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd heard there was a big exhibition\nof niche manga for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, they hold it in this kind of place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some people in my class got a booth\nat the Comic Stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:53.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:07:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we got to talking about how lame it would be\nif we only have one game to put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With only a third-rate game like that, there's\nno way any customers or anybody will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A game is a holistic work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To try to fake it by filling up holes in the game script\nwith minigames along the way is too damn cynical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell invited Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}Do you think like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the last drinking party of first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}You're all really too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were supposed to at least\ntry to invite everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}Your thinking is way too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I figured, even if I invited him, he wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}Do you hear me, all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}It's all really about how good a script you create!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, he hasn't ever come to anything before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the most crucial thing, the story, is lame,\nthe players won't bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you get even this most basic concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's the case, can you make\na more interesting one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or should I say I'm in the middle of making\none with an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In high school he was head of the Literature Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so the script is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,shall I do you the honor of\nsetting it out at your booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:08:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll teach you what a real game is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My classmates were in tears, begging for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I decided to put our game in their booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've got less than a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without a deadline, you'd just laze around\nand procrastinate, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, Sato, you know you're the one\nwho started this talk of creating a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to be a game creator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once my buzz wears off,\nwe'll get to work immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've only been given one month after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use that laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's watch each other as we work\nto keep us from procrastinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the fesrival grounds in Kasenjiki\NPark tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:05.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hot, isn't it, Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your A/C doesn't seem to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been temperamental since a little while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it finally gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HE09A91&\3c&HD99E91&\shad0\frz348.24\fscx67.5\fscy71.25\pos(209,100)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival\ngrounds in Kasenjiki park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:45.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H55&}We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival\ngrounds in Kasenjiki park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:51.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H55&}Please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, want to go to the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't have that kind of spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But wouldn't a little mood change\nincrease our work efficiency?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even so, it doesn't have to be fireworks, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No good comes out of going\nto see stupid fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finished the color design for the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dropped it into "Shared Files,"\nso give it a check, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The heroine Rei's secret is revealed in\na classroom of the hero's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have nothing. I have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:36.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, even if it turns\nthe whole world against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's, uh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why does everything turn into her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is great, Yamazaki. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before they journey off into a different world, the\nhero and Rei go to the beach to make memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, you come out here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't mind being seen if it's by you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R... Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this. How am I supposed to concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, why did she appear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, this is her first outfit when they\ngo to a different world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:47.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell has come over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, you're worried about\nreal-life romance, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki, was that her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:01.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've thought of nothing but her\nfor a while now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm thinking of her;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she just pops up in my head of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must mean you're actually in love with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:21.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm in love with a girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're ridiculous, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Girls are just human beings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All this "love" stuff doesn't exist\nin the three-dimensional world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Originally, romantic love didn't exist in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arranged marriages and late-night trysts\nwere all there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This "romantic love" stuff is a custom\nthat came in from overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Romantic love is a trap to expand\nthe capitalist system!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you're gonna let it dance you\naround like a puppet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:55.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to get on the other side of it and turn this\N"love" illusion into a way to make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say that, but what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you in love with that Nanako girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nanako's even the model for\nthis heroine, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival\ngrounds in Kasenjiki park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HC1BEDE&\3c&H7A84AD&\shad0\frx18\fry52\frz327.208\pos(251,137)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fireworks displays can just vanish from this world!\NPlease invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:46.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was on the brink of stupidly repeating\nthe same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:54.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was when I was still in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dork!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nyah-nyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dumb-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're lame-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no, Paruko's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everybody run for cover before she tells on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of here! It's Paruko! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Hold on!\NGet out of here! It's Paruko! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you calling Paruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:28.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that was my first crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I was already set to transfer schools\nwhen the first term ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:34.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I was already set to transfer schools\nwhen the first term ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I asked her to the fireworks so I'd at least\nhave a last remembrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But tomorrow I sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...sort of have to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:54.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,go see my sick grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's how my first crush ended all too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if that had really been the end,\NI might still have been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women lie with a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even that Nanako, all the while she was\nsaying she had some audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I'm positive she's on a date with another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same goes for that Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's for damn sure she's laughing at you,\NSato the hikikomori, behind your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women are a disease of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to bring down the iron hammer of Justice\nupon the world's women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Sato, say it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,G... Get lost, women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put this on and try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put this on and try again!
