Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women! Get lost, women!\NGet lost, women! Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women! Get lost, women!\NGet lost, women! Get lost, women!
