Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wonder who that is?\NGet lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HE4FFFF&\3c&H0F61A4&\shad0\fnSegoe Print\frz338.159\fscx172.5\fscy147.5\pos(203,114)}Nanako-tan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? Nanako?\NGet lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NGet lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:58.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NGet lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could you keep quiet for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello? What's up with the sudden call?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The thing is, the audition suddenly got postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, I remembered the fireworks display\nyou were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm actually at the station already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:20.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! It's no problem for me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll come to meet you there.\NWait there, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:24.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A change of mood is necessary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That being so, I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, keep working hard on that script, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can all get shot by fireworks and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still have quite a while until counseling time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, it's about today's counseling...\NI'd like to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On that note...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me to see the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:55.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\c&H007580&\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8}Sora no sukima ni, kumo no yukue ni himawari mawaru\NSunflowers spin in gaps in the sky, where clouds go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:21:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H008595&}Hanabi no you ni hanabira chireba kimi wa kakure\NWhen flower petals cascade like fireworks, you hide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\c&H009AAD&\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8}Tameiki shite\NI sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Might this not be a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:12.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H009EB6&}Kuchi wo tsuita serifu wa dame sa\NThe line that comes to my lips is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:15.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After this, I'll bet there's going to be a big backlash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:17.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H009EB6&}Uso sa, yume sa\NIt's a lie; it's a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H009FB7&}Youkoso natsu no hi\NWelcome, summer days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:33.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H00A5BE&}Nakushita natsu no e\NA lost picture of summer
