Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\an8\3c&H500A00&\4c&H000000&\4a&Hb0&\shad1.8\c&H00B4CF&}Moo ichido egakoo\NLet's draw it one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:42.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if it's this kind of trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,maybe it's all right.
