Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:15.55,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa, ababa, dancing baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.00,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.51,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.94,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,We were all loved equally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as it's supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.98,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.31,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.08,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Each destiny takes a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.38,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.02,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some can look at other's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.45,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others can't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:37.92,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some get to learn love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:39.39,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:40.99,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.42,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:45.56,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,A baby, a baby human till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:51.53,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Oh, what an adorable baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:54.50,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"I just want to love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.00,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.54,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:00.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,The baby she is holding is really a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.04,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Ababa!" I snicker to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:03.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiding in my pretended innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:05.08,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so easy to be a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:06.41,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should be one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:08.08,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa! Dance, multiply
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:09.22,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,And take it to space!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:09.98,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:10.75,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:11.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:12.15,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:13.69,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:14.46,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:16.15,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You slipped up, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The heroine's name is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:38.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to the Dark Side!"
